title: Comparison of Cortical Organoids to Human Cortex Identifies Cellular Identity and Maturation Differences
abstract: Direct Comparisons Between Cortical Organoids Generated with 3 Distinct Protocols and Primary Developing Human Cortex
overall_design: Single-cell sequencing of cortical organoids using 10X Chormium v2 and NovaSeq S2. The primary developing human cortex samples will be available through dbGaP. Project name: A Cellular Resolution Census of the Developing Human Brain
summary: Direct Comparisons Between Cortical Organoids Generated with 3 Distinct Protocols and Primary Developing Human Cortex
